'''瑞普利水族館'''（{{lang-en|Ripley's Aquarium of Canada}}），是位于[[多伦多|多伦多]]的一所水族馆。

==历史==
由{{link-en|利普瑞娱乐公司|Ripley Entertainment}}控股，水族馆由2013年10月16日对公众开放<ref name="a">{{cite news|title=Ripley’s Aquarium of Canada opens its doors|url=http://www.680news.com/2013/10/16/ripleys-aquarium-of-canada-set-to-open-wednesday/|accessdate=2013-10-25|newspaper=The Canadian Press and CityNews.ca|archive-date=2018-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103170529/https://www.680news.com/2013/10/16/ripleys-aquarium-of-canada-set-to-open-wednesday/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

瑞普利水族館位于[[加拿大国家电视塔|加拿大国家电视塔]]下，并直接与[[人行天桥|人行天桥]]相连；水族馆包含13500种海洋生物<ref name="a" />。水族馆有5.7百万公斤的水中展示着世界各地的海洋生物及环境<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.seetorontonow.com/listings/ripleys-aquarium-of-canada/#sthash.xmqvRPjN.dpuf |title=Tourism Toronto | Ripley’s Aquarium of Canada |publisher=Seetorontonow.com |date= |accessdate=2013-08-09 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020142425/https://www.seetorontonow.com/listings/ripleys-aquarium-of-canada/#sthash.xmqvRPjN.dpuf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整个水族馆分为多个部分，危险湖（{{lang|en|Dangerous Lagoon}}）和鳐鱼湾（{{lang|en|Ray Bay}}）是馆内两个最大的人工湖，危险湖容量达250万立升，长达97米的玻璃隧道和移动通道<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bharchitects.com/en/projects/127#sthash.XLtoFd00.dpuf |title=B+H Architects - Global architectural, interior, landscape, sustainability and planning design firm with offices in Toronto, Vancouver, Shanghai, Singapore, Ho Chi Minh City, Delhi, Sharjah and Dubai |publisher=Bharchitects.com |date= |accessdate=2013-08-09 |archive-date=2017-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170309073239/http://www.bharchitects.com/en/projects/127#sthash.XLtoFd00.dpuf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

